# Fans Feature - Task Summary Table

| Task Number | Task Name | User Story | Acceptance Criteria | Module/Page |
|-------------|-----------|------------|-------------------|-------------|
| Task 1 | Create On Boarding Page UI | As a new user, I want to see an attractive onboarding screen with Songcry branding so that I can understand what the app is about and feel confident to proceed. | AC 1: Page displays Songcry logo prominently<br>AC 2: App branding elements are visible<br>AC 3: Sign up button is clearly displayed<br>AC 4: Google, Facebook, and Apple sign up buttons are available<br>AC 5: Login link is accessible | On Boarding Module / On Boarding Page |
| Task 2 | Handle Sign Up Button Click | As a new user, I want to click the sign up button so that I can proceed to choose my role in the app. | AC 1: Button click navigates user to choose role page | On Boarding Module / On Boarding Page |
| Task 3 | Handle Google Sign Up Button | As a new user, I want to sign up using my Google account so that I can quickly create an account without manual registration. | AC 1: Button click redirects to Google OAuth flow<br>AC 2: If authentication successful, navigate to set username page<br>AC 3: If authentication fails, return to on boarding page | On Boarding Module / On Boarding Page |
| Task 4 | Handle Facebook Sign Up Button | As a new user, I want to sign up using my Facebook account so that I can quickly create an account using my existing social media profile. | AC 1: Button click redirects to Facebook OAuth flow<br>AC 2: If authentication successful, navigate to set username page<br>AC 3: If authentication fails, return to on boarding page | On Boarding Module / On Boarding Page |
| Task 5 | Handle Apple ID Sign Up Button | As a new user, I want to sign up using my Apple ID so that I can securely create an account with Apple's privacy features. | AC 1: Button click redirects to Apple ID flow<br>AC 2: If authentication successful, navigate to set username page<br>AC 3: If authentication fails, return to on boarding page | On Boarding Module / On Boarding Page |
| Task 6 | Handle Login Link Click | As an existing user, I want to click the login link so that I can access my existing account. | AC 1: Link click navigates user to existing user login page | On Boarding Module / On Boarding Page |
| Task 7 | Create Choose Role Page UI | GIVEN user clicks Sign Up button on the On Boarding Page, As a new user, I want to see a role selection page so that I can choose whether I'm joining as a Fan or an Artist. | AC 1: Page displays clear role selection options<br>AC 2: Fan button is prominently displayed<br>AC 3: Artist button is prominently displayed<br>AC 4: Page shows relevant descriptions for each role<br>AC 5: Navigation back to previous page is available | On Boarding Module / Choose Role Page |
| Task 8 | Handle Fan Role Selection | As a new user, I want to select the Fan role so that I can proceed to confirm my choice and access fan-specific features. | AC 1: Fan button click navigates to Fan Role Confirmation page | On Boarding Module / Choose Role Page |
| Task 9 | Handle Artist Role Selection | As a new user, I want to select the Artist role so that I can proceed to confirm my choice and access artist-specific features. | AC 1: Artist button click navigates to Artist Confirmation page | On Boarding Module / Choose Role Page |
| Task 10 | Create Fan Role Confirmation Page UI | GIVEN user selects Fan role on Choose Role Page, As a new user, I want to see a confirmation page for Fan role so that I can confirm my choice and understand what being a Fan means. | AC 1: Page displays "Are you a Fan?" title<br>AC 2: Page shows Fan role description and benefits<br>AC 3: Page displays relevant Fan icon/illustration<br>AC 4: Confirm button is prominently displayed<br>AC 5: Navigation back to previous page is available | Sign Up Module / Fan Role Confirmation Page |
| Task 11 | Handle Fan Role Confirmation | As a new user on Fan Role Confirmation Page, I want to click the confirm button so that I can proceed to set up my email. | AC 1: Confirm button click navigates to next step in registration process | Sign Up Module / Fan Role Confirmation Page |
| Task 12 | Handle Back Navigation from Fan Role Confirmation Page | GIVEN user is on Fan Role Confirmation Page, As a new user, I want to click the back button so that I can return to the Choose Role Page. | AC 1: Back button is visible and accessible<br>AC 2: Back button click navigates to Choose Role Page<br>AC 3: Previous role selection state is maintained | Sign Up Module / Fan Role Confirmation Page |
| Task 13 | Create Set Username Page UI | GIVEN user completes Fan Role Confirmation, As a new user, I want to see a username setup page so that I can create a unique username for my account. | AC 1: Page displays "Set Your Username" title<br>AC 2: Username input field is prominently displayed<br>AC 3: Username validation feedback is shown in real-time<br>AC 4: Continue button is available when username is valid<br>AC 5: Navigation back to previous page is available | Sign Up Module / Set Username Page |
| Task 14 | Handle Username Input Validation | As a new user on Set Username Page, I want to see real-time validation of my username so that I know if my chosen username is available and meets requirements. | AC 1: Username must be at least 3 characters long<br>AC 2: Username must be unique (not already taken)<br>AC 3: Username can only contain letters, numbers, and underscores<br>AC 4: Real-time feedback shows availability status<br>AC 5: Error messages are clear and helpful | Sign Up Module / Set Username Page |
| Task 15 | Handle Continue Button from Set Username Page | As a new user on Set Username Page, I want to click the continue button with a valid username so that I can proceed to complete my account setup. | AC 1: Continue button is only enabled when username is valid<br>AC 2: Button click saves username to user profile<br>AC 3: Button click navigates to next step in onboarding process | Sign Up Module / Set Username Page |

---

**Summary:**
- Total Tasks: 15
- On Boarding Module: 9 tasks (Tasks 1-9)
- Sign Up Module: 6 tasks (Tasks 10-15)
- Pages Covered: On Boarding Page, Choose Role Page, Fan Role Confirmation Page, Set Username Page

*Note: This table provides a comprehensive overview of all tasks in the Fans Feature documentation for easy reference and project management.*
